634aef-821c-f21b-59ac-0cc7a17bebd5-92daa75b\" class=\"w-layout-grid team-profile-large_portfolio-header_metatag-list\"><div id=\"w-node-_46634aef-821c-f21b-59ac-0cc7a17bebd6-92daa75b\" class=\"team-profile-large_portfolio-header_metatag-item\"><h3 class=\"secondary_tag\">Job role</h3><div>Consultant </div></div><div id=\"w-node-_46634aef-821c-f21b-59ac-0cc7a17bebe4-92daa75b\" class=\"team-profile-large_portfolio-header_metatag-item\"><h3 class=\"secondary_tag\">Contact number</h3><div>07932 021 689</div></div><div id=\"w-node-_46634aef-821c-f21b-59ac-0cc7a17bebe9-92daa75b\" class=\"team-profile-large_portfolio-header_metatag-item\"><h3 class=\"secondary_tag\">Email</h3><div>acameron@moonstone.co.ug</div></div><div id=\"w-node-e8c50d8f-b3d6-889d-250d-a52eda171395-92daa75b\" class=\"team_tags-wrapper\"><div class=\"tag-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div role=\"list\" class=\"tag-list w-dyn-items\"><div role=\"listitem\" class=\"tag-item w-dyn-item\"><a href=\"/for-businesses/regulatory\" class=\"primary_tag w-inline-block\"><div>Regulatory </div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"team-profile-large_portfolio-header_image-wrapper\"><img data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"0.05\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"team-profile-large_portfolio-header_image\" src=\"/assets/155.png\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"team-header_background-icon-wrapper-copy\"><img data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"-0.25\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" class=\"team-header_background-icon-copy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/6924418b395e9ab3d12cfac8_shape-2.svg\"></div><div data-hidden=\"live\" class=\"dark_background\"></div></header><header class=\"section_team-profile-large_header-1\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid team-profile-large_header-1_content\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-left\"><h2>Committed to delivering the best outcome for you</h2></div><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-right\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><p>Andrew Cameron is an experienced Solicitor specialising in Business Crime and Regulatory matters.</p><p>‍</p><p>He began his career as a police station adviser before qualifying as a Solicitor in 2001. Early in his career, Andrew represented clients accused of criminal and motoring offences, providing advice and support at police stations and in the Magistrates&#x27; Court.</p><p>‍</p><p>Over time, his practice has evolved to focus on business crime and regulatory investigations. Today, he advises and represents both individuals and businesses facing intervention, investigation or prosecution by a range of enforcement authorities, including:</p><ul role=\"list\"><li>Police</li><li>HMRC</li><li>Health and Safety Executive</li><li>Local Authorities</li><li>Environment Agency</li><li>Fire and Rescue Authorities</li><li>Information Commissioner</li><li>Care Quality Commission</li></ul><p>‍</p><p>He provides clear, practical advice during what can often be complex and high pressure situations, helping clients understand their position and navigate the process with confidence.</p><p>‍</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></header><section class=\"section_expertise-video w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"wrapper_wide-screen is-light\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"expertise-video_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid expertise-video_content\"><div class=\"expertise-video_content-left\"><h2 class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty\"></h2><p class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty\"></p></div><div class=\"expertise-video_content-right\"><div class=\"expertise-image_wrapper\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/plugins/Basic/assets/placeholder.60f9b1840c.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"image w-dyn-bind-empty\"></div>